Continue a project that started in 2022 

Develop an app for an Amazing Race-style game 

The game will serve as a fundraising and community activity for primary school students and families 

The project is for Black Hill Primary School 

The fundraising idea involves engaging in an “amazing race” style game 

The app will be used with smart phones or tablets 

The game will allow students and their families to engage and complete tasks in and around the school district 

The aim is to reduce the need for a large volunteer base or employees to pay 

The team started the project in 2022 

The client is based in Ballarat. 
